{1: '1', 2: 'Bianca', 3: 'Why is the stage decorated this way?', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Bianca', 3: "It feels like a church, except it's lighter...", 4: '1'}
{2: "It's said that these places were for people to hang out together in spring back in the Golden Age.", 3: '7'}
{2: 'Bianca', 3: 'Spring? I should have put on a more fitting coating, then.', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Bianca', 3: "Mine doesn't feel suitable for a place like this.", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Bianca', 3: 'Regardless, thank you for choosing me to enter the maze with you, Commandant.', 4: '1'}
{2: "You don't have to be so polite here.", 3: '12'}
{2: 'Bianca', 3: 'Does this place call for... a little more intimacy?', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Bianca', 3: 'I don\'t know what to call you except for "Commandant", though.', 4: '1'}
{2: 'You can call me by my name.', 3: '17', 4: "That's okay.", 5: '21'}
{3: 'Bianca rarely says your name, from what you can recall.'}
{2: 'Bianca', 3: 'Hmm... I feel more comfortable calling you Commandant.', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Whatever you like, Bianca.', 3: '21'}
{2: 'Bianca', 3: 'In that case... Commandant?', 4: '1'}
{3: 'Slightly surprised by your answer, Bianca pauses for a second before smiling.'}
{2: 'Bianca', 3: "I don't know why, but I always feel safe when I'm with you.", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Bianca', 3: "No matter how short our time together is, I always feel like I don't have to worry about the future afterward, no matter how difficult it may be.", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Bianca', 3: 'Although our paths are different, memories like this...', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Bianca', 3: 'Make me happy.', 4: '1'}
{2: 'I also like to spend time with you, Bianca.', 3: '29'}
{2: 'Bianca', 3: "My break isn't over yet. Do you want to head to the beach down there with me?", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Bianca', 3: 'We should be able to continue our wonderful time together...', 4: '1'}
